reviewText:
a very beautiful movie with a strong message about true love, giving, influencing other persons for good by just being happy in doing what you love... and the best part is that it is based on a true story.
In these days of insanity and confusion,, this is GOOD NEWS.
It is an amazing film, full of grace. Every Christian should see this film.
